title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-15-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-15-2013 MON






The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET  

   
The Glenn Beck Program - 7-15-13

Monday, July 15, 2013 10:24 AM

Joe Pags fills in for Glenn Beck today and brings the heated debate all over the nation 
 right to the Blaze,
 breaking down the reaction to the Zimmerman trial verdict.

  Joe calls out the race baters and tells it like it is.

  Also, the death of journalism, 
  at least that's how Joe see's as he discusses how a live prank on air could have been avoided
 if the anchor actually read what she was about to read and not just taken it verbatim
 right off the teleprompter.
